{"tid":317991,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【Content Farm】UTravel 9UP當秘笈 教你睇飛機型號","createTime":"2017-07-11T23:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T08:28:54.000Z","uid":36551,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd25195ba2106fd43b112db60d7997adcc99f11","tid":317991,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:14:44.000Z","msg":"【#UTravel旅遊盲點】飛機號碼 A380、A330 代表乜？ 5 個 航空業的 飛機型號 小秘密<br />\n文 : U Travel 小編 旅神 Joy<br />\n2017.07.11<br />\n<a href=\"http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/DetailNews.php?id=ADgRYREhA3QMLg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2FDetailNews.php%3Fid%3DADgRYREhA3QMLg&d=Hjxnf1Uv6oAoTQJOP%2F3ZeYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e5a580c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/DetailNews.php?id=ADgRYREhA3QMLg</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，明眼人都睇出成篇文大部份內容都係抄維基百科，依D碎料就唔再講，話明係Content Farm，左抄右抄當食生菜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係有D料連維基百科都冇，咁就要靠 旅神 Joy 9UP喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/063024_4fe0a90c6ab7f298ec5200df28442d0a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F063024_4fe0a90c6ab7f298ec5200df28442d0a.JPG&h=63663e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA380本身個Project係叫A3XX，推出時揀咗A380係因為「8」同雙層客艙嘅外型好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: <a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=rfpsBQAAQBAJ&amp;lpg=PP1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;pg=PA79#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DrfpsBQAAQBAJ%26lpg%3DPP1%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26pg%3DPA79%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse&d=Hjxnf1Uv6oAoTQJOP%2F3ZeYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=317a1fda\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=rfpsBQAAQBAJ&amp;lpg=PP1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;pg=PA79#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/063602_54d1353a6bdbef5edea5f33ef8e7bc02.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F063602_54d1353a6bdbef5edea5f33ef8e7bc02.JPG&h=1465e5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依段仲離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一，707唔係波音第一款客機，只係第一款噴射客機，人地出707之前已經造咗幾十年螺旋槳客機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二，揀個「7」字只係因為2-6已經俾波音其他產品用咗，去到推出噴射客機時咁啱去到「7」，而波音又覺得第一款噴射客機叫波音700唔夠搶眼，所以就改咗做707<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: <a href=\"http://www.boeing.com/news/frontiers/archive/2004/february/i_history.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boeing.com%2Fnews%2Ffrontiers%2Farchive%2F2004%2Ffebruary%2Fi_history.html&d=Hjxnf1Uv6oAoTQJOP%2F3ZeYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5ad259fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boeing.com/news/frontiers/archive/2004/february/i_history.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實依D料Google search都好易搵到，咁都可以講錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool-gif.com/media/gif/3c/dd/3cdda5e9124a7a6cbb089259fe62d94c/cool.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool-gif.com%2Fmedia%2Fgif%2F3c%2Fdd%2F3cdda5e9124a7a6cbb089259fe62d94c%2Fcool.gif&h=330317b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcf7847ce19b376db03ab61da2c26a798026123f","tid":317991,"uid":12543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d293ea46f04c21e8dab49d24ecd2439ffd661de5","tid":317991,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"依d page真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922a16b870777071d833a0d91701cb0e2aef5e43","tid":317991,"uid":55513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd4114b0927a12b26aafa3943c8d804de3ffd27","tid":317991,"uid":839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"Call鳩假期報導下"}]}